==English==

===Etymology===
From '''[[hand]]''' + '''[[-some]]'''. It at first meant ''[[dexterous]]''; compare Dutch '''[[handzaam]]''', ''dexterous'', ''ready'', ''limber'', ''manageable'', and English ''[[handy]]''.

